          <Vi>Câu (trong ngữ pháp); bản án, hình phạt</Vi>
          <En>A grammatical unit of words that expresses a complete thought; a judicial punishment imposed on a convicted defendant.</En>
          <Example>The judge announced the sentence after the jury reached a verdict.</Example>
